  <brief_title>Intravenous Iron in Gynecologic Cancer Patients Receiving Chemotherapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevention of Blood Transfusion With Intravenous Iron in Gynecologic Cancer Patients Receiving Platinum Based Chemotherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
