  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 20-70 years

          -  Good performance status (Zubrod score &lt; 2)

          -  No serious underlying disease

          -  Normal renal function test

          -  Normal liver function test

          -  Platinum based chemotherapy is the first line regimen

          -  No prior or receiving radiotherapy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Iron hypersensitivity

          -  Underlying disease which has the risk of iron overload such as chronic kidney disease,
             major thalassemia

          -  Progressive disease

          -  Bone marrow metastasis
      </textblock>
